```

### API Endpoint:
```
POST /api/heralds
Body: { herald: string, input: string, userId: string }
Response: { success: boolean, type: string, response: string, ... }
```

### Environment Variables Required:
```
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...  // Required for AI responses
```

